Nutrient data for: 45000177, Swanson, SWANSON BROTH VEGETABLE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 10051000156355

ORGANIC VEGETABLE BROTH (PREPARED FROM WATER AND CONCENTRATED JUICES OF CARROT*, ONION*, CELERIAC*), CONTAINS LESS THAN 2 % OF THE FOLLOWING: SEA SALT, FLAVORING, COOKED ORGANIC VEGETABLES (CARROT*, ONION*, CELERY*), ORGANIC PEAR JUICE FROM CONCENTRATE (WATER, ORGANIC PEAR JUICE CONCENTRATE), ORGANIC YEAST EXTRACT (ORGANIC YEAST EXTRACT, SALT, WHEAT*), SUGAR*, CANOLA OIL*, FLAVORING, CARROT POWDER*, ONION POWDER*, POTATO FLOUR*, BLACK PEPPER*. *CERTIFIED ORGANIC Date available: 12/31/2004 Date last updated by company: 01/01/2015
